Porcelain and wood flooring create a clean and worry free living space. The open kitchen boasts newer appliances, granite countertops matched with tumbled travertine accents and upgraded cabinetry. Bathrooms feature granite vanities, designer paint colors, whirlpool tub in the master. Recent replacement of roof and HVAC (7 yr) add to the tremendous value. Come and see quick, you will not be disappointed!!
